{"tid":1790255,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Cyberpunk-香港的空想未來","createTime":"2019-12-20T01:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T10:54:51.000Z","uid":128680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"38ae9811e5ded4feb100a65cd229c8adbf304e2c","tid":1790255,"uid":128680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:11:56.000Z","msg":"Cyberpunk- Umbrella and Water<br />\n<br />\n前言<br />\n2019年，為著名數碼龐克作品《アキラ》及《Blade runner》當中所設定的年份。兩者皆描述約30年後的世界，近未來風格再加點異想天開的科技，當中是包含著對未來世界的幻想、反烏托邦和叛逆元素。而對香港而言，2019年只是叛逆的開始，Cyberpunk年代即將來臨。2019年6月9日，為流水抗爭的開端並持續了百多日，但不論抗爭成功與否，數碼龐克年代依舊會來臨。考慮過去堅尼系數走勢及2019年後需重振經濟等因素，30年後的香港或會處於更嚴重的「貧者越貧，富者越富」狀況。加上近十年的科技發展速度突然加快，可預見30年後整個香港社會會進入「High tech low life 」的模式，亦即是所謂的數碼龐克年代。本文旨為對往後約30年那可見可預測的未來進行有根據的分析並考慮與&ldquo;烏托邦&rdquo;抗衡的方向。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n若想了解更多，㩒啦屌<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1RnmcCkjU9950agPnOddxhjNyPygqAHzP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1RnmcCkjU9950agPnOddxhjNyPygqAHzP&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5cjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=82fec71d\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1RnmcCkjU9950agPnOddxhjNyPygqAHzP</a>"},{"pid":"826f5085a10d1bb86e41df10882ce267ebb98721","tid":1790255,"uid":128680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:41:40.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"076f15ded17b495f5fcb7cb223570faa1b35af20","tid":1790255,"uid":128680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:41:54.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"faaf50ea3b631359043c852f6309ea75d90980e4","tid":1790255,"uid":128680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:42:11.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"ed707d6372e1d87608f8f0601afc691d48f1b9e9","tid":1790255,"uid":128680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:42:43.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"7bf8e63fe7cafdccc830b9459d7795ec42ac6de3","tid":1790255,"uid":128680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,